snippet.title: Atticus TheDeathMetaller
snippet.description:
ATDM is an aspiring Film maker who loves to rant on what's on his mind.  Weather it be SJWism, Religious dumbasses, Metal, Film, or anything that is warranted on what to talk about.

I have three series that I focus on
TDMR (THeDeathMetaller Reviews)
TDMC (TheDeathMetaller Cinemas)
TDMH (The Death Metal Historian)

Make sure to Subscribe for more content, keep it Metal and have a wonderful day.  \m/ \m/
